                },
                "description": "Get live performance metrics for a strategy.\n\nAll counts and drawdown values are anchored to **day 1** = the timestamp of the earliest `strategy_performance` snapshot for this strategy (dynamic per strategy, NOT a hard-coded date).\n\nField semantics:\n- `totalTrades`: trades with `entry_time >= day1` (any status).\n- `winningTrades` / `losingTrades`: closed trades with `pnl > 0` / `pnl < 0`, since day 1.\n- `winRate`: `winningTrades / total_closed_trades`. Open and cancelled trades are excluded from both numerator and denominator.\n- `maxDrawdown`: largest peak-to-trough drop on `strategy_performance.total_pnl` since day 1, in **absolute USD** (non-negative). Monotonic — never decreases.\n- `currentDrawdown`: `peak_so_far − latest_total_pnl` in absolute USD (non-negative). 0 when latest snapshot is the all-time peak.\n- `totalPnL` / `unrealizedPnL` / `realizedPnL`: live values from `real_time_strategies`.\n\n`totalReturn` is intentionally absent — it requires an account-level baseline which is out of scope for the strategy endpoint."
