                "description": "Seed deterministic demo data for local testing.\n\n**Wipes every existing strategy** (and their `strategy_performance`, `trades`, `real_time_strategies`, `real_time_trades` rows), then creates **10 fresh strategies** named `Strategy 1` through `Strategy 10`. Each gets a 10-day `strategy_performance` snapshot series plus a mix of closed/open/cancelled trades shaped to exercise different chart patterns (uptrends, oscillating ranges, drawdown-heavy, etc.). The Postgres sync triggers auto-populate the `real_time_*` mirror tables.\n\n**Disabled in production** — the controller returns 403 when `NODE_ENV === 'production'`.\n\nBody (optional):\n- `dayOne` (YYYY-MM-DD) — overrides the day-1 anchor. Defaults to `2024-04-20`.\n\nResponse: an array of 10 per-strategy results, each containing `name` (`Strategy N`), `strategyId`, counts, and the URLs (`performanceUrl`, `publicSummaryUrl`) you can hit next."
